{"tid":928283,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple 心急救亡   名嘴騷狂送 iPhone XR 谷人氣","createTime":"2018-12-04T17:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T10:13:21.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bc0535b36ad683301ff758b42e52bfa394af076e","tid":928283,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T17:17:03.000Z","msg":"最近一直有消息指 Apple 錯估新 iPhone 的需求，尤其是 iPhone XR 更是重災區，Apple 需要 Cut 單保平安。雖然 Apple 高層早前接受訪問時指 iPhone XR 銷量最佳，但實際上他們卻要借助名嘴 Ellen DeGeneres 的節目宣傳以增加人氣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2018-12/03/211954/uniqlo_1_1220ca90bc45e8ca4c34e43375b04ed2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2018-12%2F03%2F211954%2Funiqlo_1_1220ca90bc45e8ca4c34e43375b04ed2.jpg&h=975083c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了配合聖誕主題，Ellen DeGeneres 一向會在節目大手筆，接連 12 天向觀眾送出禮物。當然這些禮物都是各大品牌贊助，以達到宣傳效果。在日前播出的節目，Ellen 和她的嘉賓 Julia Roberts 向在場觀眾送出一人一部 iPhone XR，而 Ellen 亦識做地介紹 iPhone XR 的人像自拍模式、6 色機身選擇和 iPhone 中最佳電力 3 大賣點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KpwvwQmtElY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKpwvwQmtElY&d=qmBz6ZN77ZI7cUQ0dYhunp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ed2ed14f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KpwvwQmtElY</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然 Ellen 以往不時在節目中拿出 iPhone，不過她最讓人印象深刻的應該是當奧斯卡頒獎典禮時，拿出 Galaxy 手機找大牌明星自拍一幕。如果 iPhone XR 的銷量非常好，相信 Apple 未必需要借助名嘴騷送手機谷人氣。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：9to5mac"},{"pid":"aae7ddb2a0a9ed6ec5e62a10e6778fbfc0894588","tid":928283,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T17:34:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f7426f3948120b6336f6391a5aac345d2a2161a","tid":928283,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T17:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae7cd6675beb2d1a1772c19128570869e9d2f62","tid":928283,"uid":68478,"like":38,"dislike":5,